site_name: Land at Fleet Street Hill, Shoreditch, London E2 6EE
description: Comprehensive re-development of the Site to provide two buildings and a pavilion building together delivering Purpose Built Shared Living Accommodation (Sui Generis), affordable housing units with associated communal amenity space (Use Class C3), a flexible commercial space (Use Class E) and the delivery of wider public realm improvements comprising hard and soft landscaping and other associated works.
